preference.name: MERelationTypePartsOtherAssigned
preference.preference_description: Defines the relation (occurrence) types that Teamcenter interprets as other product actions; that is, actions other than consumption, handling, assembly, and disassembly for operations and assignment for processes. Valid Values: An array of strings, where each string represents a relation (occurrence) type.
